            "text": "<p>I’ve tried tons of supplements and vitamins. I’ve tried thousands of exercise routines and bought thousands of dollars worth of fitness gear. I’ve spent hundreds of hours researching how to optimize my mind and my body. That’s why this brand exists. </p><p>After many years of trying to find what clicks for me, I also discovered that I couldn’t get what I wanted in one place.</p><p>Now I can, because I created it. I think there are lots of people out there like me, and so I think you’ll find this brand useful too.</p><p></p><p>The Fit Nerd is a brand owned by Make It So, LLC.</p>",
